The film is based on Roald Dahl's classic children's tale and is a remake of 1971's "Willy Wonka & the Chocolate Factory."

programme.title: Minions

Stars Jane Fonda and Jack Lemmon were Oscar-nominated for Best Actress and Best Actor.

programme.title: The Unfaithful

programme.desc: Best Picture nominee is an expose of scandal-mongering newspapers and their effect on innocent people. An editor who's hounded by publishers to ramp up circulation attempts to do so by reinvestigating an old murder case, and tragedy follows.

programme.title: The Barkleys of Broadway
programme.desc: Fred Astaire and Ginger Rogers reunited after 10 years for this tunefest about a successful musical-comedy team who break up when she decides to become a "serious" artist.
